outputs.output_descr: This project  aims at organizing and sensitizing farmer groups in targeted areas, provide modern and affordable land preparation and extension services. In addition to this, the project will provide machinery to support farmers in agricultural land opening through subsidized arrangements.To achieve this, the project shall establish and operationalize a project management unit. These interventions are expected to result in enhanced social security through increased and improved food production.
